node.text:
Eat the best pizza New York has to offer with a VIP experience! 🍕 Get tickets to New York Bucket List Pizza Tours at the link in our bio @NYbucketlist 🍕: @rubirosa_nyc Famous Tie-Dye Pizza 
Visit bit.ly/nypizzatours for tickets and information
Presented by @bucketlisters

node.text: Tag your NYC happy hour crew! 🍻☀️🍹Pull up a seat & crack open a @CoronaUSA – We’ve rounded up 12 of the happiest happy hour spots in the city. SWIPE to see some of our favorites and find the full list at Bucketlisters.com or our link-in-bio! #newyork #Partner

node.text: Tag who you’re splitting this seafood tower with! 😍🦞🦪 The iconic French steakhouse @BoucherieNYC has everything from a raw bar to burgers, an array of cocktails (absinthe, anyone?) & most importantly in this summer heat: a high-tech cooling system. Check our link-in-bio for reservations! #NewYork #Partner

node.text: Il Patio di Eataly is open for the summer - Tag a friend you want to dine with! 🌸🍽️🌼 Take a seat on @EatalyFlatiron’s outdoor patio inspired by Italian piazzas in the summertime, with their new menu of "great" items like salumi e formaggi boards as long as far as the eye can see and antipasti perfect for sharing with the table. Check our link-in-bio for full details & reservations! #NewYork #Partner

node.text: Have you seen the new @StellaArtoisUSA Pop-Up at Pier 15? 🍺🍕 More than a place to dine, it features 6 of New York's beloved chefs & restaurants each putting their own unique spin on one of the city's most iconic dishes...Pizza! Grab your friends and take in summer from one of the prettiest spots in the city, all while sipping Stella of course 😋 See our stories for more info + reservations. (Running through Aug 19) #Ad #seaportArtois #newyork_instagram
